Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H5A2C8D&\c&HE5D7DF&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(702,622,698,474,0,667)}才不是偶爾吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H607692&\c&HD1D4E2&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(192,637,192,594,0,167)}果然是美食家W
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我要被你們指責到這個地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&HB542A7&\c&HF2C6EE&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(676,220,676,-45,0,1400)}居然一頓午飯就吃了3000圓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H526387&\c&HD4E0EE&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(981,340,981,-90,0,2150)}也太不瞭解民情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H72A072&\c&HD4F4D0&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(276,351,276,-20,0,1900)}首相就那麼了不起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H7F4D40&\c&HF2D8CA&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(809.143,486.857,809.143,-34,0,2650)}我的午飯才300圓(淚)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H8B374D&\c&HFED4DF&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(332,499,332,-18.571,0,2550)}真是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼的吧 不就3000圓的燉牛肉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H71904D&\c&HD1DDC7&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(1045.714,682.286,1045.714,81,0,3040)}一臉燉牛肉樣!
