Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H6089AA&\c&HDFEAF3&\shad0\fn微軟雅黑\move(772.571,499.429,772.571,236.714,0,1300)}哈?態度真差啊
